 boy took a nickname when he went to get justice for the crimes that the mayor was responsible for. He leaves the note stating that it was Leone the superhuman who killed the mayor.</p></div><div id="p4"><p>The police checked the CCTV cameras to find the face of the criminal. The boy started to kill the sinners who played a role in the murder of the mayor. The boy did his efforts to hide the evidence, that linked him to the mayorâ€™s murder. This gave the boy an ulterior motive to make a second strike towards the vice mayor. The police arrive at the scene of the vice mayor's murder. The vice mayor used to send government officials to collect taxes. When the farmers or the locals were not able to afford the tax. So, many of them started to take their own life.</p></div><div id="p5"><p> The boy who kept killing the drug traffickers, mafias, corrupt cops, etc. When the boy heard the whereabouts of these people. He started to murder the sinners who committed these crimes. Then he stayed low-key to avoid suspicion by the locals and the town folk. Government officials heard the scream of a woman who had been widowed. This caused tension in the townspeople who had witnessed the crime. The police started to take a statement from the witnesses on the scene.</p></div><div id="p6"><p>This caused people to panic about the tragedy caused by the young boy. He has the urge to kill the sinners. This kept him going on and on about murdering people. This caused him to lose control over murdering innocent people. He makes his move at night   </p></div><div id="crime"><img src="Crime.jpeg" alt=ðŸ’£><img src="crime.jpeg" Alt="ðŸ˜€"><img src="criminal.jpeg" Alt="ðŸ˜ƒ"><img src="Crime scene.jpeg" Alt="ðŸ˜Š"><img src="crime scene1.jpeg" Alt="ðŸ˜‹"><img src="crime scene2.jpeg" Alt="ðŸ˜‚"><a href="#crime">Crime</a></div><a href="A3-3.html"> Next chapter</a></body></html>